            "title": "NICE Non-GAAP EPS of $3.18 beats by $0.01, revenue of $732M beats by $3.04M",
            "description": "<html><body><ul>\n<li>NICE <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/pr/20305598-nice-reports-13-percent-year-over-year-cloud-revenue-growth-for-the-third-quarter-2025-and\">press release</a>  (NICE): Q3  Non-GAAP EPS of $3.18 <font color=\"green\"> beats by $0.01</font>.</li>\n<li>Revenue of $732M (+6.1% Y/Y) <font color=\"green\"> beats by $3.04M</font>.</li>\n<li>AI ARR increased 49% year over year, 43% excluding Cognigy</li>\n<li>\n<p data-eci=\"true\">The Company is raising its full-year 2025 non-GAAP total revenues to be in an expected range of $2,932 million to $2,946 million, representing 7% year over year growth at the midpoint compared to full-year 2024.</p>\n<p>The Company is updating full-year 2025 non-GAAP fully diluted earnings per share to be in a range of $12.18 to $12.32, representing 10% year over year growth at the midpoint compared to full-year 2024.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</body></html>",
